00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
If they work for it, we need to pay them as a nation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
That's the bottom line: paying people what they've earned and worked for is honorable.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
If they work for it, they deserve a check.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
They work hard, and it's wrong not to pay people.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
The FAA is working for it; they keep us protected and watch over us as we're flying.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
It's just common sense.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
And these RINOs, the Lord said to pray into that group.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
There's softness, but there's influence on them through blackmail.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
'You do what we tell you to do,' I hear them saying.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
The Lord said to pray for that group because there's some softness there that you can work with.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
The Lord said those are the ones you can work with.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
I saw this group of people leaning toward voting the right way, but they're facing great influence and pressure from others.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
'You do this, or we're going to make sure you don't get reelected.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
' It's blackmail and outside pressure regarding money funding their campaigns.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
They should flip parties anyway and say, 'We're done with you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
' They stand for what they stand for, but they know what's right, and paying people their wages is right.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
They have a conscience, partially.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
Some of the things they stand for are wrong, but the Lord said that's what you need.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
I'm just telling you what the Holy Spirit says, so that's what we're going to continue to pray for.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
I challenge you as we close tonight: you have an assignment.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We're praying for the hearts of about seven of them to change.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I'm trying to count them.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
There was one behind, but I'm praying for these people to change.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I saw men and women.
